{"updated_at": "2012-03-02T19:52:25Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-03-02T01:05:53Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4278344", "id": 4278344, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5217", "issue_id": 5217, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/patrick99e99", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "648553f5c693d93c9ea2e042857ad22c", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/648553f5c693d93c9ea2e042857ad22c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F25b6a534a8c88b8e73fe7b865fd36bde.png", "id": 28946, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/events{/privacy}", "login": "patrick99e99", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/followers"}, "body": "The difference is, with namespacing the actual data in the serialized object is not changed, just the accessor methods...  For example:\r\n\r\n    >@stuff.item[:color]\r\n    => \"blue\"\r\n\r\n    >@stuff.item_color\r\n    => \"blue\"\r\n\r\n    >@stuff.thing[:color]\r\n    => \"purple\"\r\n    \r\n    >@stuff.article_color\r\n    => \"purple\"\r\n\r\nThat's what the point of this patch is...", "_id": {"$oid": "52381b25bd3543c15100e3b3"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5217#issuecomment-4278344"}
